Package <Unnamed>

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddEditAppointmentPanel
    Class implementing the Add/Edit/View panel which opens when a cell is clicked on the calendar grid.
    Appointment
    Base class for implementing an Appointment structure.
    AppointmentBook
    The AppointmentBook class is a wrapper class for the Appointment class.
    CalendarPane
    CalendarPane is the class which forms the outer container for the components required to manipulate a specific AppointmentBook.
    CalendarTable
    Class to provide the bulk of the functionality of the 'grid style' calendar.
    CreatePanel
    CreatePanel is a panel which facilitates the creation of new AppointmentBook objects and adding them to the GUI global booksList.
    DatabaseCommunicator
    A static class to handle the additional functionality offered by storing the AppointmentBook objects in a database.
    HelperMethods
    Static class implementing various methods which dont fit anywhere else in the code structure at present.
    Main  
    MainFrame
    Class for setting up the JFrame in which the rest of the JPanels will be placed.
    MonthViewPanel
    MonthViewPanel class implements the 'grid style' monthly calendar layout which allows the user to manually search through the AppointmentBook content.
    myTableModel
    Basic class to customise the DefaultTableModel to make the calendar grid JTable not editable.
    SelectPanel
    SelectPanel adds the GUI and functionality to access currently tracked AppointmentBook objects.
    WelcomePanel
    WelcomePanel sets up the first content pane used for the GUI.
